  "original_title": "\u0dbb\u0dd4\u0dc3\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dcf\u0db1\u0dd4 \u0dad\u0dd9\u0dbd\u0dca \u0dc3\u0db8\u0dcf\u0d9c\u0db8\u0dca \u0db1\u0dd2\u0dba\u0ddd\u0da2\u0dd2\u0dad\u0dba\u0db1\u0dca \u0daf\u0dd9\u0daf\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dd9\u0d9a\u0dca \u0d9a\u0da7\u0dd4\u0db1\u0dcf\u0dba\u0d9a\u0da7",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Two representatives of Russian oil companies to Katunayake",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Two representatives of Russian oil companies had arrived at Katunayake Airport this morning (07th) to discuss fuel supply to Sri Lanka.",
        "The two had arrived at Katunayake Airport at 9.00 am on 07/07 on Gulf Air flight GF-144 from Bahrain.",
        "Due to the suspension of international direct flights between Moscow in Russia and Katunayake in Sri Lanka, these representatives had come to Katunayake via Bahrain.",
        "National Freedom Front leader Wimal Weerawansa MP and a group of others came to Katunayake Airport's special guest room to welcome the two."
      ],
